Access article under the CC BY 4.0 license. Published by Elsevier Ltd.. All 
rights reserved.

DOI: 10.1016/S2214-109X(21)00299-0
PMCID: PMC8415897
PMID: 34487685 [Indexed for MEDLINE]

Conflict of interest statement: Declaration of interests We declare no competing 
interests.


772. Lancet Neurol. 2021 Oct;20(10):795-820. doi: 10.1016/S1474-4422(21)00252-0.
