Global, regional, and national burden of stroke and its risk factors, 1990-2019: 
a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2019.

GBD 2019 Stroke Collaborators.

Collaborators: Feigin VL, Stark BA, Johnson CO, Roth GA, Bisignano C, Abady GG, 
Abbasifard M, Abbasi-Kangevari M, Abd-Allah F, Abedi V, Abualhasan A, 
